			<h3>Easy Customization</h3>
			<p>Customize Pico with over 130 CSS&nbsp;variables, or dive deeper by using SASS. Switch between 20 handcrafted color&nbsp;themes and compose with 30+ modular&nbsp;components to tailor the UI to your brand's look&nbsp;and&nbsp;feel.</p>
