			<h3>Optimized Performance</h3>
			<p>Speed meets elegance. Unlike bulky and overcomplicated frameworks that demand extensive&nbsp;class overrides and JavaScript, Pico keeps your HTML lean, decreases memory usage by avoiding excessive CSS specificity, and reduces loaded files.</p>
